    "notes": "Number.prototype.toString(radix) and codepoint-based comparison must be locale-independent. localeCompare without an explicit locale can vary by host ICU data, so a portable applet uses plain < / > on code units (pinned here) — toLocaleString/localeCompare(locale-sensitive) are a deliberate divergence trap avoided."
